---
// Layout.astro - Hanya Maintenance Banner
---

<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Maintenance Mode</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --maintenance-bg: #ff6b6b;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html, body {
        height: 100%;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      }

      body {
        background-color: #000;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      /* Maintenance Banner */
      .maintenance-banner {
        background-color: var(--maintenance-bg);
        color: white;
        padding: 20px 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 15px;
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 90%;
      }

      .maintenance-banner span {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Maintenance Banner -->
    <div class="maintenance-banner" id="maintenanceBanner">
      <span>ðŸš§</span>
      <p>Website ini sedang dalam pemeliharaan (maintenance)</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
